{"tid":1003936,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳淑莊稱已向立法會秘書處提出引用特權法查沙中綫事件","createTime":"2019-02-01T05:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T05:15:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"effa11748935e6ad29131a6b9d0aa5a77cf3871a","tid":1003936,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1440902-20190131.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1440902-20190131.htm&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2Fco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=e1fba3ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1440902-20190131.htm&h=29e5caea\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1440902-20190131.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n陳淑莊稱已向立法會秘書處提出引用特權法查沙中綫事件<br />\n<br />\n2019-01-31 HKT 14:04<br />\n 分享工具\t facebook  twitter<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1440902_1_20190131142246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1440902_1_20190131142246.jpg&h=d50205c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳淑莊指今日已向立法會秘書處遞交初稿，預計最快下月15日於內務委員會討論。（陳沛聰攝）<br />\n<br />\n沙中綫紅磡站工程再發現問題。公民黨立法會議員陳淑莊表示，會提出引用權力及特權條例調查事件。她指，今日已向立法會秘書處遞交初稿，但仍有少許修訂，預計最快下月15日於內務委員會討論。<br />\n<br />\n對於經民聯盧偉國建議，擴大沙中綫獨立調查委員會的職權範圍，以調查新發現的施工問題。陳淑莊質疑，為何要再由調查委員會主席夏正民處理，而不運用議員的權力。"},{"pid":"f9ecb816e776553ccaea40375c047834af30ddf4","tid":1003936,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"浪費時間"},{"pid":"33dbce472ac1bf69c657ef29cc30d103f61741a3","tid":1003936,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"建制一定否決"}]}